    "We argue that LLMs metrics are informative only when there are sufficient input representations for LLMs to abstract patterns from.",
    "Therefore, we complement LLMs metrics with investigations of frequency.",
    "We acknowledge that including a dependency parser might lead to a rather complex pipeline.",
    "However, we maintain that this inclusion is necessary, since degree expression is sophisticated, understudied, and there is avoidance and underuse among L2 learners.",
    "As far as our knowledge goes, there is no published engineering tool in how to automatically identify degree expressions."
